{"tid":2275429,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"流感急增一倍 何栢良︰危險訊號","createTime":"2020-11-07T06:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:10:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e519c616bdd0c6650d8dc4b12b24ef72f6bb3826","tid":2275429,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/RWO3MJXJWZF4JA57UP7RLOJ65Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FRWO3MJXJWZF4JA57UP7RLOJ65Q%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuMQVtcXcndjic5JqfcA1BWo%3D&h=7a7bb89b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201107%2FRWO3MJXJWZF4JA57UP7RLOJ65Q%2F&h=411632c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201107/RWO3MJXJWZF4JA57UP7RLOJ65Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n流感急增一倍 何栢良︰危險訊號<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o9hNW2_y50tYyXrcv1_9qk9s31A=/1766x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LRLGXFAMENF4HF44P7GRMLWUGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo9hNW2_y50tYyXrcv1_9qk9s31A%3D%2F1766x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLRLGXFAMENF4HF44P7GRMLWUGI.jpg&h=94b9e763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何栢良指近期向私家醫生求診的病人中，流行性感冒病類個案急增一倍，是危險訊號。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】小學及幼稚園接連爆發上呼吸道感染，元朗太陽島英文幼稚園有34名學童染病。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良表示，近期向私家醫生求診的病人中，流行性感冒病類個案急增一倍，是危險訊號。港人防疫意識鬆懈，增加病毒傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保就業擸1.65億 港機逼減薪15%  稱計劃屬「自願」拒承諾不裁員<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨公佈，元朗太陽島英文幼稚園爆發上呼吸道感染，涉及17男童和17女童，年齡介乎3至5歲。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良指出，。。。。。。。。。，比率增加約一倍。他形容已出現危險訊號。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳旅議會財困 裁16人賣物業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料防疫鬆懈 社交聚會多<br />\n<br />\n他估計，幼稚園及學校的爆發並非在校內傳播，因學校已實施嚴格防感染措施，而這些群組於10月25日即假期後出現，不排除有部份學生放學後或假期時參加課外活動或家庭之間聚會而感染。他相信是過去兩周假期下，港人心態上放鬆了，多了外出及社交活動，其間有除下口罩，造成傳播。<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情方面，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良指出，本港10月初至本周三錄得174宗輸入個案，當中機師及機組人員共18宗，約佔10%，比例偏高，而前天一宗本地個案的患者是飛機維修員，本港須加強對機組人員的防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，雖然本港已對從多個地方入境者實施上機前要有檢測陰性證明，抵港後再檢測，但仍有多個航班同一機有逾五人確診，令人關注會否有地方的陰性證明造假，而本港沒規定轉機也要有同樣要求。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫學會指，即使本地疫情得到控制，但如患者入境時不檢測，就會引致輸入個案出現，並會在本地傳播，故此入境旅客的隔離檢疫豁免應盡量減少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wvFX-poM4p-ne4wT__7jbT3-zNc=/3098x685/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OHHGFB232NDNPHYZLNN4Z5YNNM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwvFX-poM4p-ne4wT__7jbT3-zNc%3D%2F3098x685%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOHHGFB232NDNPHYZLNN4Z5YNNM.gif&h=f463430d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15fd48686511e86bc67a882cdf77d2fe47430ce5","tid":2275429,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2932459548b3a6162c6bdc650f74552a8c28508d","tid":2275429,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"上年同期有幾多單先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"}]}